data.description: ''MOTIVATED SELLER''  Tranquil Pool home in Highly-desirable community of Ridge Manor Estates, Merritt Island. Marvelously located close to Port Canaveral, Beaches, Merritt Island, and Beachline to Orlando & MCO. This lovely 3bd/2ba home has countless updates, including: Hurricane rated Windows and Garage Door, (w/ new opener); New Kitchen: Cabinets, Quartz Counters, Stainless-steel Appliances, Sink, Faucet, & Disposal. New: Vinyl-plank floors, Ceiling fans, Raised Panel Doors and updated Bathrooms. Interior painted 2019, Exterior in 2023. New Attic Insulation .  Screened Pool has new Filter & Programmable Pump.  Large 1 car garage includes Front-load GE Washer & Dryer (included), and Door to Side yard.  There's a new 13 x 8 foot premium Shed in backyard.
